-- =====================================================
-- Alaska (AK) Medical Malpractice Rules
-- Enhanced Verification Protocol v2.0
-- =====================================================
-- State: Alaska
-- Governing Law: AS 09.55.536 et seq. (Medical Malpractice Actions)
-- Negligence Model: PURE COMPARATIVE FAULT (AS 09.17.060)
-- SOL: 2 years from discovery (AS 09.55.560(a))
-- Non-economic Damage Cap: $250,000 standard; $400,000 for wrongful death or >70% disability (AS 09.55.549)
-- Expert: Required per AS 09.55.540
-- =====================================================

-- RULE 1: STANDARD OF CARE
